import React from "react";
import { Box, Grid, TextField } from "@material-ui/core";
import HeaderTask from "./../Home/Tasks/HeaderTask";

export default function Profile() {
  return (
    <Box className="body-admin m-0 pt-5 bgr-admin" sx={{ minHeight: "100vh" }}>
      <Grid container spacing={1} className="ps-4 w-100">
        <Grid item xs={8}>
          <Box className="box">
            <HeaderTask
              bgr="badge-purple"
              title="Edit Profile"
              position="start"
              caption="Complete your profile"
            />
            <Grid container spacing={2} className="py-4 px-3">
              <Grid item xs={6}>
                <TextField
                  label="Company (How2Code)"
                  disabled
                  variant="standard"
                  className="w-100"
                />
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={3}>
                <TextField
                  color="secondary"
                  label="Username"
                  variant="standard"
                  className="w-100"
                />
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={3}>
                <TextField
                  label="Email address"
                  color="secondary"
                  variant="standard"
                  className="w-100"
                />
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={6}>
                <TextField
                  label="First Name"
                  color="secondary"
                  variant="standard"
                  className="w-100"
                />
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={6}>
                <TextField
                  label="Last Name"
                  color="secondary"
                  variant="standard"
                  className="w-100"
                />
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={4}>
                <TextField
                  label="City"
                  color="secondary"
                  variant="standard"
                  className="w-100"
                />
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={4}>
                <TextField
                  label="Country"
                  color="secondary"
                  variant="standard"
                  className="w-100"
                />
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={4}>
                <TextField
                  label="Postal Code"
                  color="secondary"
                  variant="standard"
                  className="w-100"
                />
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={12}>
                <TextField
                  label="About me"
                  color="secondary"
                  variant="standard"
                  className="w-100"
                />
              </Grid>
            </Grid>
          </Box>
        </Grid>
        <Grid item xs={4}></Grid>
      </Grid>
    </Box>
  );
}
